issue.title: Add Python script for SpatialSense on Raspberry Pi
issue.body:
This script can be run on the Raspberry Pi Zero using 
Python.  The speaker will beep when the user crosses 
the threshold distance to any object in front of them.  
The rate of the beeping will increase as the user gets 
closer to the object.
